episodes.title: Eligio Bishop rape trial: Cult expert [Rick Alan Ross] testifies
episodes.description:
A cult expert took the stand in the rape trial of Eligio Bishop, the accused sex cult leader. A former member of the Carbon Nation cult accused Bishop of raping her and posting illicit images of her to social media. The latest on the trial.

episodes.title: Accused cult leader Eligio Bishop turns down plea deal | FOX 5 News
episodes.description:
Eligio Bishop, the accused leader of the Carbon Nation cult, turned down a plea deal, it was revealed on Thursday. He is charged with rape, false imprisonment, and sharing sexually explicit content on social media.
